local Manager = s_WordDictionaryDatabase; Manager.allwords["somnambulist"]={"somnambulist","[səm'næmbjʊlɪst]","[ sɔm'næmbjulist, səm- ]","n.梦游者",'n.梦游者','In the day, he went around like a somnambulist, with absent stare, gazing upon the world he had just discovered.','白天，他像一个梦游者似地走东走西，目光恍恍惚惚的，目不转睛地望着他这新发现的世界。','A somnambulist can happily combine sleep and exercise.','梦游者能把睡眠和运动巧妙地结合在一起。'}
